uk.co.unitycoders.pircbotx.data

Class JavaObjectStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.unitycoders.pircbotx.data.JavaObjectStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectStorage

    public class JavaObjectStore
extends Object
implements ObjectStorage
    Java native object serialisation. The simplest form of persistent storage is serialisation. This class uses the in built serialisation system to create files on the system for classes which need to persist over many runs of the bot.
